* **`<html>`** â†’ Root element of the document.
* **`<head>`** â†’ Contains metadata and links CSS files.
* **`<link>`** â†’ Connects external CSS file and Bootstrap.
* **`<body>`** â†’ Contains all visible content.
* **`<div>`** â†’ Used for background container (`.bg`) and card container (`.card-container`).
* **`<h1>`** â†’ Displays main heading (â€œHappy Mealsâ€).
* **`<p>`** â†’ Displays description text under the heading.
