# ğŸ”¹ CSS Properties I Used

* **`background-image`** â†’ Sets hero section background.
* **`background-size`** â†’ Ensures the background covers the container fully.
* **`height` / `width`** â†’ Controls size of background and card containers.
* **`font-family`** â†’ Applies custom fonts like Roboto and Bree Serif.
* **`font-size`** / **`font-style`** / **`font-weight`** â†’ Styles heading and description.
* **`color`** â†’ Sets text color for heading, description, and button.
* **`padding`** â†’ Adds spacing inside card container and button.
* **`border-radius`** â†’ Rounds corners of card container and button.
* **Bootstrap Flex (`d-flex`, `flex-column`, `justify-content-end`)** â†’ Positions the card at the bottom of the page.
* **`background-color`** â†’ Colors the card container and button for contrast.

